name: it is mandatory others are optional
value: what value insert in name,
expire: storing data on cookie is not permanent,
path: where we have to make cookie available ,like \home, \about
domain: cookie is not available cross domain  subdoman: where we make to make cookie accessible,
secure: works on https not work on http,
httponly: only accessible if we make server call not assible on ui


